eight: normal; border-spacing: 1px; "><span style="width: 43px; ">Limited Edition of 1938</span></span></div><div style="line-height: 19px; margin-top: 10px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-spacing: 0px; " class="itemtext" align="center"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: normal; border-spacing: 1px; "><span style="width: 43px; ">Materials: Mohair</span></span></div><div style="line-height: 19px; margin-top: 10px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-spacing: 0px; " class="itemtext" align="center"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: normal; border-spacing: 1px; "><span id="_ctl0_ContentPlaceHolder1_Label2" style="width: 43px; ">EAN:</span>&nbsp;682391</span></div><div style="line-height: 19px; margin-top: 10px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-spacing: 0px; " class="itemtext" align="center"><strong style="text-align: left; ">New in its original box</strong></div><div style="line-height: 19px; margin-top: 10px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-spacing: 0px; " class="itemtext" align="center"><strong style="text-align: left; "><font color="#ff0000">I will ship worldwide. Domestic shipping is included. Please email me for international shipping rates. I will combine shipping if you purchase more than one figurine.</font></strong></div><div style="line-height: 19px; margin-top: 10px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-spacing: 0px; " class="itemtext" align="center"><strong style="text-align: left; "><font color="#ff0000">PLEASE EMAIL ME WITH ANY QUESTIONS.</font></strong></div>
